; Test compare_by_commodity with same numeric price but different currencies
; Covers commodity.cc lines 433-434 (recursion found no difference, comparing
; prices with commodity for ordering by commodity name)

2024/01/01 Buy in USD
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash        $-1500.00

2024/01/02 Buy in EUR at same numeric price
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {150.00 EUR}
    Assets:EUR         -750.00 EUR

test bal --no-total --lots Brokerage
   10 AAPL {$150.00}
 5 AAPL {150.00 EUR}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
